{
  "texts": [
    "-Constraint: The walk should take place in a public space in a summer day.",
    "-Text: As John strolled through the park one crisp autumn morning, he noticed the usual red and gold leaves blanketing the path.",
    "Today, however, a stray dog, thin and shivering, approached him.",
    "He hesitated, then offered his hand for the dog to sniff.",
    "It flinched at first, but soon warmed up to him."
  ]
}